{"tid":334155,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"曹星如落實10月7日鬥日本拳王","createTime":"2017-07-24T12:46:20.000Z","updateTime":"2017-07-25T05:02:54.000Z","uid":20933,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"14b4971ccac237fb32a120ffad849492b9b96780","tid":334155,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-24T12:46:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/e-paper/20170310/large/1489127300_d3aa.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20170310%2Flarge%2F1489127300_d3aa.jpg&h=4708f5e7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n「神奇小子」曹星如（21-0-0，13KOs）鐵定於今年10月7日在香港會展上演的《王者對決3》與日本拳王河野公平對壘，比賽將會進行12回合對決。<br />\n<br />\n前WBA超蠅量級世界拳王河野公平昨晚於日本東京後樂園場館出戰，並以5回合TKO擊敗泰國拳手，取得挑戰WBO超蠅量級國際冠軍的資格。河野公平生涯戰績33勝1和10負、14次K.O.對手的河野，是於今日正式與香港拳擊推廣人、DEF Promotions創辦人兼總監劉志遠簽訂比賽合約，他坦言昨晚勝出後整晚都睡不著，十分期待10月對星如的比賽。至於將會爭取22連勝的曹星如今日接受訪問時，首先恭喜河野公平勝出了昨晚的比賽，他透露自己7月中已重新投入訓練，現時確定了10月會出戰河野，他說︰「可以有明確方向去作針對性訓練，希望在即將到來的這次比賽可發揮更佳水平。」<br />\n<br />\n劉志遠表示：「我們早於2015年已希望安排曹星如與當時仍為世界拳王的河野公平對決，可惜因種種原因錯過讓星如挑戰世界冠軍的機會，然而正因此令港日兩地拳迷對這場拳賽引頸期待。」劉志遠續指：「星如未來有機會挑戰現任世界拳擊協會(WBO)超蠅量級世界拳王、外號『怪物』的井上尚彌(13-0，9KOs)，而河野公平亦曾與井上尚彌作賽，我們也希望藉今場賽事，作為星如的一個測驗，了解雙方差距，作為未來的參考。」<br />\n<br />\n外號「Tough Boy」的河野公平現年36歲，2015年10月於美國芝加哥擊敗曾為兩個量級世界拳王、當時被譽為日本拳擊第一人的龜田興毅，成功衛冕WBA超蠅量級世界拳王金腰帶。河野於2000年正式出道進入職業拳擊，2008年首次挑戰世界冠軍寶座，經驗老到。<br />\n<br />\n同日另一場賽事，其中今年5月13日曾經在香港出戰DEF Fight Night 15的東太平洋拳擊聯邦（OPBF）超雛量級拳后後藤亞由美（7-0-0，5KOs），也將再次來港參賽，對手暫時未公佈。"},{"pid":"50e5a05b65ba78f51fea204a0a6ae89cba5ee1c8","tid":334155,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-24T12:47:00.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?guid=56995833&amp;category_guid=7032049&amp;category=instant&amp;issue=20170724\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fguid%3D56995833%26category_guid%3D7032049%26category%3Dinstant%26issue%3D20170724&d=vR6pTwvDyohvV2q5r7FjduI2ZYfPb188nwqbwuz8hpE%3D&h=79a2edf8\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fguid%3D56995833%26category_guid%3D7032049%26category%3Dinstant%26issue%3D20170724&h=2f171c2b\" target=\"_blank\">http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?guid=56995833&amp;category_guid=7032049&amp;category=instant&amp;issue=20170724</a>"},{"pid":"daf75ebb0db49b0d7271c1bff8803af0910c9ad3","tid":334155,"uid":59898,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-24T12:48:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />唔知個post有冇人應呢，留名"},{"pid":"a4f4affa5dee60878526589170a8100ee01961c8","tid":334155,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-24T12:49:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"01757564e695ded91250f3414ab1d05cc8e770ac","tid":334155,"uid":693,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-24T12:49:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cf7cfb2ccaf4ac7b365e4d44e2839e33c1267a52","tid":334155,"uid":53466,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-24T12:50:24.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"b8b7dc1418a597a2e51ba2c8dd8ff6a02ba72899","tid":334155,"uid":20933,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-24T12:53:53.000Z","msg":"打河野公平講咗兩年終於成事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6d1925ec929cdc55dc893f87f3aebd957ef483cf","tid":334155,"uid":810,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-24T13:24:38.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>打河野公平講咗兩年終於成事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n小心揸車啲好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ca10ed10d8f1a29e5fb62c028f9e92ece593e4db